articles.author: Michael Idato
articles.title: Ukraine wins Eurovision after ‘irregular voting patterns’ delay count - Sydney Morning Herald
articles.description: A dramatic end to Europe’s iconic singing competition saw Australia in 15th place, the UK as a potential 2023 host and organisers dealing with an attempt to disrupt the voting.
